&lt;h2 id="conclusion">Conclusion&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>This guide detailed how to schedule Lambda functions using AWS EventBridge. Keep in mind that leaving the EventBridge setup as is will incur charges, so be sure to delete it when it&amp;rsquo;s no longer needed.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>